{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">I need to head home......This must be the place I want to return to.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;The Path Home&quot; is a mysterious\u00a0puzzle game with a 2D pixel-art style, where you gradually transform a mysterious world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Players can use panels to &quot;<strong>flip</strong>&quot; between black and white.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3409620/extras/rule1.gif?t=1737681485\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The girl is focused on going home, so she\u2019s always looking for the &quot;<strong>shortest route to the goal</strong>.&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It\u2019s up to you to reshape the puzzle world and guide her to the goal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But if there are <strong>fake goals</strong>, she might get fooled.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Block the fake paths or steer her away from them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3409620/extras/rule2-1.gif?t=1737681485\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3409620/extras/rule2-2.gif?t=1737681485\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The <strong>crow</strong> is your friend.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Lead the girl on a detour to help her reunite with the crow.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3409620/extras/rule3.gif?t=1737681485\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The tiles you flip aren\u2019t limited to black and white \u2014 new types will appear as you progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph